THAT IDENTIFIES EACH GRANT FOR WHICH:
(I) NO PART OF THE GRANT IS UNDER CONTRACT APPROVED BY
THE BOARD; AND
(II) THE BOARD HAS NOT ENCUMBERED MONEY FOR ANY PART
OF THE GRANT.
8–128.
(a) [If, within 2 years after the date of an authorization of State debt, evidence that
